item.title: The darwin awards - A Chronicle of Enterprising Demises
item.description: The darwin awards - A Chronicle of Enterprising Demises Came across this due to my good friend Mr. Samir … well it turns out that there is an award for people who do wierd stuff and end up seriously injured or dead. I salute the guy who is running this … who says there is no humor in death :). Honoring those who improve the species…by accidentally removing themselves from it!
